q: Why not XML?
a: Do the XML - create the better library.

q: Why "const byte * buf, int len"?
a: Because the FFD are intended to be short and simple; because a streaming
   parser brings nothing but more code to the table.

q: Why not hard-linked to the windlib (an implicit gear at my "h3r" project)?
a: Because enforcing you using my List<T> instead of yours, is wrong.